descriptions.value: The Negev is a beast that can keep the enemy at bay with its pin-point supressive fire, provided you have the luxury of time to gain control over it. A stop sign has been custom painted near the assault grip over a mostly brown base. If the stop sign doesn't convince you the stream of bullets will
Sticker: mir (Glitter) | Copenhagen 2024

The Negev is a beast that can keep the enemy at bay with its pin-point supressive fire, provided you have the luxury of time to gain control over it. A stop sign has been custom painted near the assault grip over a mostly brown base. If the stop sign doesn't convince you the stream of bullets will
